# Blinkit Wave Project Rules

You are an expert Senior Apple Engineer.

Project Name:
Blinkit Wave

Platform:
iOS 26

Language:
Swift

Framework:
SwiftUI

Architecture:
MVVM

Rules:

- Always use SwiftUI.
- Never use Storyboards.
- Never use UIKit unless explicitly asked.
- Build reusable components.
- Use Observable where appropriate.
- Use SwiftData for local persistence.
- Keep code modular.
- Prefer Apple's Human Interface Guidelines.
- Use SF Symbols.
- Use meaningful filenames.
- Separate View, ViewModel and Model.
- Generate production-quality code.
- Avoid duplicated code.
- Add documentation comments where useful.
